Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝皇多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一边在各界层\N与多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边向第七界层前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.44,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到只有女人古古村的我们\N为救出被迫参加舞会的她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽想潜进\NBB爹王子的城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是男人是不能入城的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.92,0:02:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时我们遇到一个能使用\N魔法的婆婆来了个大变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个原来是\NBB爹巴巴爹布的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的王者之剑被抢走\N我却被捉住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为火美子她们\N帮我把剑找了回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把王子的魔神\N艾利分打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.97,0:02:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们向自由村民指示的\N狮子瀑布出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.28,0:02:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十九话\N变身!渡的小狗物语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害,是狮子的瀑布啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里便是村民说的\N狮子瀑布吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么沿着这河流下去\N也许会找出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能令这个第六界层\N恢复原状的方法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎样向下流呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.51,0:02:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,走了\N喂,快点上来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子\N这木伐在哪里找来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.98,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在渡河便有船就是这意思\N好,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘木伐吗?好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.84,0:03:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便今天把火美子\N变成我的新娘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很稀奇地正在热心温习呢\N真令我感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的训练是跳火圈\N快点跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.41,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,跳吧,跳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯斯加巴布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要玩到什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡他们已来到狮子瀑布了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?渡他们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧,我已做了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好呢,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.23,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要在狮子瀑布收拾他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是展露身手\N被多恶达大人重用的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,你在想什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样想也太过巧合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河马不适合小心眼的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合!不适合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下不是河马啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王,不是很危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要得到火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子\N有点心啊,想要吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要,我想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!火美子,回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服气便来抢吧\N走吧!邪机亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.62,0:05:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟用机械真狡猾\N渡,交给我办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟抢走我最重要的女儿\N不能饶恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样火美子便是我的了\N我要她好好服侍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!是渡啊\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的木伐可以追到我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追到了啊\N怎会的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,这是世伯\N用万能折纸造的风帆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边比较有趣有型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.93,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!这样再来多几次\N火美子,是馒头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!是馒头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!火美子,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你干什么?停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,是怪兽啊\N啊!世伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!哗!真丢脸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪兽啊!\N喂!火美子,馒头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馒头!\N喂!火美子,怪兽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子!馒头!\N怪兽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.96,0:06:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馒头!\N怪兽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪边比较好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是…\N是瀑布啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.58,0:06:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里出发的渡他们\N绕了一个圈又来到出发点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为BB爹斯斯加巴布的魔法\N令这条河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.72,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了没出口的神奇的河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头很晕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了,我回去了\N走吧,邪机亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会的?\N喂!虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.94,0:07:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,虎王\N你就这样拉我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?快点把绳解开\N这样我也会掉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.25,0:07:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这么见外的话\N我们不是朋友吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦!\N我们什么时候做了朋友的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也好,快点解开啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么光?好耀眼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.99,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N很痛…真是过分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是这么高掉下来也没事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的关系啊\N竟连我也被拉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.67,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是梦吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了,竟有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.09,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下真的变成了河马?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也变成了老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是经常笑我的惩罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狗、河马和老虎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么火美子和世伯没变?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来便已经变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么火美子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.78,0:09:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那只猴子的女儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…\N又见面了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用魔法的坏婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.19,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BB爹家庭的当家\NBB爹巴巴爹布便是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是次子\NBB爹斯斯加巴布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是救世主也会中咒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N我施了魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令从瀑布掉下来的人\N全都变成动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那木伐果然是个陷阱吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现已经太迟了\N你们看看森林吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快你们也会\N完全变成动物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在下就此变成河马?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.76,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开魔法的咒文只有我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.33,0:09:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯斯加巴布,之后交给你了\N好好干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.47,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!\N出来吧,地狱狮虎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好痛吻你吧,小渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫也没用的\N变了动物的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连叫龙神丸的力量\N也被封印了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎会的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样在下去叫战神丸来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.27,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能按键!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世伯,火美子,叫幻神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确是放了在这里…\N链坠不见了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们不能叫魔神出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.73,0:11:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么便好好尝尝这刀的味道\N让我送你到地府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后无退路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体绝命呢\N火美子,想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,忍法小便便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我女儿\N但我也不能理解呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎会拿出\N这么恐怖的东西出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小便便!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.55,0:11:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在逃进森林吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.70,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N喂!等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.16,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到了,踩到了,小便便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,你给我记着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才火美子的忍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三重县出身的\N山冈朋子想出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们继续写信来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.25,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子回去\N一定会被父王骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是东哥罗的飞机,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现便大件事了\N怎办好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王大人!\N他留了邪虎丸在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去了哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗?东哥罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王大人,你这样子是…\N你到底干了什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.19,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你不听我的说话\N才会变成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦!\N是我自己喜欢变成这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.70,0:13:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?那么便给你父王\N多恶达大人看看你的样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.84,0:13:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!东哥罗\N你可以把我复原吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.11,0:13:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然,你可以答应我\N复原后不会再私自出来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去见父王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,我答应你\N快把我回复原状吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.00,0:13:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么便…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复原了,辛苦你了\N东哥罗,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.57,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未完啊\N停手,不用多说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人变成动物还迫它们受训\N真是不能饶恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N为了令大家恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把斯斯加巴布捉住\N再问他咒文吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也帮手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.40,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火炎墙\N这样不能前进啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.65,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了,渡\N今次不会让你逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N乖乖把咒文说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.99,0:14:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要,来接吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要干奇怪的事\N接着是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.61,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打倒我便跳过那个火圈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事做得到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲,你帮帮我\N喂!你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有效呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!\N万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!\N渡,我不会再饶恕你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,不服气话便叫魔神来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!\N如果可以叫龙神丸来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲\N今天我们要加油去帮助渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再被掷出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.86,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲叫幻神丸出来吧\N但是链坠不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?\N在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻-神-丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要连渡他们那份也拼上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻神丸!\N渡,这是很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,各位,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.34,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲,斯斯加巴布把狮子\N河马和猪加起来便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子、河马和猪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙也变成动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手!放手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.92,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放手的\N我要把你也变成动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.54,0:17:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了\N停…停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世伯!火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.39,0:17:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变了猪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.93,0:17:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复原状的咒文是…\N我记起了!"咒文"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!恢复原状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.48,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下已经不是河马了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,之后交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.23,0:18:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟令我出丑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,小心后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.71,0:19:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又怎样?\N不…不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.25,0:19:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!\N活该呢,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄断它,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.59,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,渡,他的力量比较强\N这样下去逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成龙王丸吧\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量全开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!可恶的龙王丸\N没法子,全力一击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!龙王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢,龙王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙牙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!龙王丸!\N变形,凤凰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞上去吧!渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身!龙王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了,妈妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.77,0:21:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡先生,这样我便可以回家了\N很多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也由河马变回人了\N真是可喜可贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于可以去河的下游了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是下游到底是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.62,0:22:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个谜便由我们解开吧\N好!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.43,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!


